  ('disabled-23e15ae5-moex-00080', 'disabled-23e15ae5', 'disabled-23e15ae5-moex-113-f162a9a1', 'sub-disabled-23e15ae5-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有一資料表R(a,b, c,d)，已知功能相依b->c，表示c功能相依於b，其中 底線字為主鍵，斜體字為外部鍵，則將其作第二正規化（2NF）的結果為：', '["R1(b,c)，R(a,b,d)", "R1(b,c)，R(a,d)", "R1(a,d)，R(a,b,c)", "R(a,b,c,d)"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "0389d105f1be", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9919953e41f1", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "504", "s": "1414", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "計算機大意", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "電腦打字"}'::jsonb, NULL),
